{%- comment -%}
  MY.LAB logo block — remplace le bloc <td class="shop-name__cell"> dans le header.

  HOW TO APPLY:
  1. Dans le template "Confirmation de commande", chercher :
       <td class="shop-name__cell">
         {%- if shop.email_logo_url %}
           <img src="{{shop.email_logo_url}}" alt="{{ shop.name }}" width="{{ shop.email_logo_width }}">
         {%- else %}
           <h1 class="shop-name__text">
             <a href="{{shop.url}}">{{ shop.name }}</a>
           </h1>
         {%- endif %}
       </td>
  2. Remplacer par le bloc ci-dessous.

  LOGIQUE :
  - Priorité 1 : shop.email_logo_url (si renseigné dans Notifications → Personnaliser)
  - Priorité 2 : shop.brand.logo (le logo de l'identité de marque — celui déjà uploadé)
  - Fallback : texte "MY.LAB" stylé
{%- endcomment -%}

<td class="shop-name__cell">
  {%- if shop.email_logo_url %}
    <a href="{{ shop.url }}" style="text-decoration: none;">
      <img src="{{ shop.email_logo_url }}" alt="{{ shop.name }}" width="{{ shop.email_logo_width | default: 160 }}" style="max-width: 180px; height: auto; display: block;">
    </a>
  {%- elsif shop.brand.logo %}
    <a href="{{ shop.url }}" style="text-decoration: none;">
      <img src="{{ shop.brand.logo | image_url: width: 360 }}" alt="{{ shop.name }}" width="140" style="max-width: 140px; height: auto; display: block;">
    </a>
  {%- else %}
    <h1 class="shop-name__text" style="font-family: 'DM Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.02em; margin: 0;">
      <a href="{{ shop.url }}" style="color: #111111; text-decoration: none;">MY.LAB</a>
    </h1>
  {%- endif %}
</td>
